import Container from "@mui/material/Container";
import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";
import Card from "@mui/material/Card";
import MKBox from "components/MKBox";
import MKTypography from "components/MKTypography";
import MKButton from "components/MKButton";
import MKInput from "components/MKInput";
import Header from "components/Header";
import Footer from "components/Footer";

function BecomePlayer() {
  return (
    <>
      <Header />
      <MKBox sx={{ paddingTop: "60px" }} bgcolor="white">
        {/* Hero Section */}
        <MKBox
          minHeight="50vh"
          width="100%"
          sx={{
            backgroundImage: `linear-gradient(rgba(128, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(128, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/images/soccer-player.jpg')`,
            backgroundSize: "cover",
            backgroundPosition: "center",
            display: "grid",
            placeItems: "center",
          }}
        >
          <Container>
            <Grid container justifyContent="center" textAlign="center">
              <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
                <MKTypography variant="h1" color="white" mb={3}>
                  Become a Player
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="body1" color="white" mb={3}>
                  Join our program and take your soccer career to the next level
                </MKTypography>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Container>
        </MKBox>

        {/* Application Process */}
        <Container sx={{ py: 6 }}>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <MKTypography variant="h3" mb={3}>
                Application Process
              </MKTypography>
              <MKBox mb={3}>
                <MKTypography variant="h6" mb={2}>
                  1. Submit Your Application
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="body2" color="text">
                  Fill out the application form with your personal details and soccer experience.
                </MKTypography>
              </MKBox>
              <MKBox mb={3}>
                <MKTypography variant="h6" mb={2}>
                  2. Skills Assessment
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="body2" color="text">
                  Our scouts will evaluate your technical abilities and potential.
                </MKTypography>
              </MKBox>
              <MKBox mb={3}>
                <MKTypography variant="h6" mb={2}>
                  3. Interview
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="body2" color="text">
                  Meet with our team to discuss your goals and commitment.
                </MKTypography>
              </MKBox>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <Card sx={{ p: 3 }}>
                <MKTypography variant="h4" mb={3}>
                  Apply Now
                </MKTypography>
                <MKBox component="form" method="post" autoComplete="off">
                  <Grid container spacing={3}>
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                      <MKInput
                        variant="standard"
                        label="First Name"
                        fullWidth
                        required
                      />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                      <MKInput
                        variant="standard"
                        label="Last Name"
                        fullWidth
                        required
                      />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={12}>
                      <MKInput
                        variant="standard"
                        label="Email"
                        fullWidth
                        type="email"
                        required
                      />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={12}>
                      <MKInput
                        variant="standard"
                        label="Phone"
                        fullWidth
                        type="tel"
                        required
                      />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                      <MKInput
                        variant="standard"
                        label="Age"
                        fullWidth
                        type="number"
                        required
                      />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                      <MKInput
                        variant="standard"
                        label="Position"
                        fullWidth
                        required
                      />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={12}>
                      <MKInput
                        variant="standard"
                        label="Current Club/School"
                        fullWidth
                      />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={12}>
                      <MKInput
                        variant="standard"
                        label="Tell us about your soccer experience"
                        multiline
                        rows={4}
                        fullWidth
                      />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={12}>
                      <MKButton
                        variant="contained"
                        color="error"
                        fullWidth
                        type="submit"
                      >
                        Submit Application
                      </MKButton>
                    </Grid>
                  </Grid>
                </MKBox>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </MKBox>
      <Footer />
    </>
  );
}

export default BecomePlayer;
